import React from 'react'
import Footer from '../components/Footer'
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar'
import CalendarWithExercises from '../components/CalendarWithExercises'

const Routine = () => {
  return (
    <>
        <Navbar/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'monday'}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'tuesday'}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'wednesday'}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'thursday'}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'friday'}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'saturday'}/>
            <CalendarWithExercises dayString={'sunday'}/>

         <Footer/>
    </>
    )
}

export default Routine
